categories: Category:Imperial Army officers of the Sith Empire

nodes.text: Saka'Tsesh was a female Human who served as an officer in the Imperial Army of the reconstituted Sith Empire during the Galactic War against the Galactic Republic. During the Quesh war on the planet Quesh, she was stationed at the Imperial Garrison.
Saka'Tsesh appears in the video game Star Wars: The Old Republic, released by BioWare in 2011, as a Social Items Vendor for Imperial players on Quesh.
